{"tid":2198265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸軍演逼近挑釁 台︰絕不退縮","createTime":"2020-09-11T08:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T08:36:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acd8d628c7c49f6941defec1eeba37ea446d35e3","tid":2198265,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200911/IRMWOAYCUFE6VFYO5BF5HI4IF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200911%2FIRMWOAYCUFE6VFYO5BF5HI4IF4%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fsrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=5c9810a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200911%2FIRMWOAYCUFE6VFYO5BF5HI4IF4%2F&h=cd01e5aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200911/IRMWOAYCUFE6VFYO5BF5HI4IF4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n大陸軍演逼近挑釁 台︰絕不退縮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fjcTLSdPo1UgU3b_9OXnYnZVi7o=/1276x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YITA23E5SFBJ5FQW6744ITNHSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfjcTLSdPo1UgU3b_9OXnYnZVi7o%3D%2F1276x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYITA23E5SFBJ5FQW6744ITNHSQ.jpg&h=ee6fd526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩岸關係瀕臨危險關頭，解放軍在台海不間斷進行軍演，已到了隨時擦槍走火的地步。台國防部及外交部昨晚罕見地分別召開臨時記招，國防部批評，解放軍連續兩日在台灣西南進行軍演，距台最近僅90浬（約166公里），痛斥中共「嚴重挑釁」。外交部也嚴厲譴責中共挑釁，強調台灣面對威脅絕不退縮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國務次卿月中訪台<br />\n<br />\n國防部情次室次長楊靜瑟證實，前日起連續兩日，中國海軍、空軍從早到午，以蘇30、殲10、運8等戰機，配合海軍船艦，進入台灣防空識別區進行聯合軍演，台軍派兵全程應處。國防部副部長張哲平批評，解放軍嚴重影響區域和平，強調不要低估台軍保家衞國決心。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人歐江安批評，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時，有台媒報道，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"}]}